<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٦٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4875">عَمْرُو بْنُ عَوْنٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1041">ثَابِتٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«اسْتَقْبَلَهُمُ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَلَى فَرَسٍ عُرْيٍ مَا عَلَيْهِ سَرْجٌ فِي عُنُقِهِ سَيْفٌ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>